cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with semantic segmentation of road scenes using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an unsupervised learning approach for adapting pre-trained segmenters to new cities. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing intelligent systems for road scene analysis. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with adapting road scene segmenters for autonomous vehicles. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing images and videos from Google Street View.
